 Breheny  ."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["As a boy's name this represents a revival of Middle English <i>Jan</i>, a by‐form of   John  , or an adoption of the common European form with this spelling. As a girl's name it is a short form of names such as   Janet   and   Janice ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"John Broun was born in Sauchie, Clackmannanshire, Scotland, United Kingdom. He married Gelise Shaw in 1500, in Sauchie, Clackmannanshire, Scotland, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died about 1530, in his hometown."},"et":{"–ABT 1530":"–umbes 1530","–1530":"–1530","1500–1547":"1500–1547","       1500":"1500","1547":"1547","1500":"1500","ABT 1530":"umbes 1530","1530":"1530","of Finderlie and Balquharn, Kincardine, Scotland":"Kincardineshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Sauchie, Clackmannan, Scotland":"Sauchie, Clackmannanshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–ABT 1530":"–noin 1530","–1530":"–1530","1500–1547":"1500–1547","       1500":"1500","1547":"1547","1500":"1500","ABT 1530":"noin 1530","1530":"1530","of Finderlie and Balquharn, Kincardine, Scotland":"Kincardineshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Sauchie, Clackmannan, Scotland":"Sauchie, Clackmannanshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–ABT 1530":"–environ 1530","–1530":"–1530","1500–1547":"1500–1547","       1500":"1500","1547":"1547","1500":"1500","ABT 1530":"environ 1530","1530":"1530","of Finderlie and Balquharn, Kincardine, Scotland":"Kincardineshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Sauchie, Clackmannan, Scotland":"Sauchie, Clackmannanshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"John Broun est né à Sauchie, Clackmannanshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé Gelise Shaw en 1500, à Sauchie, Clackmannanshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé environ 1530, dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"–ABT 1530":"–um 1530","–1530":"–1530","1500